reviews.text:
I like the interior decor and the dining atmosphere there.  Food in there is delicious too.... Highly recommend mixed seafood in soup and suckling pig, really nice.  Deep fries seafood, is freah, too, especially the squid.  Perfect with the dressing.

But ....... but.... dessert is the weakest part.  Chocolate cake is just like a cut brownie cubes with coconut ice cream.... really disappointed.    Strawberry cheesecake is also bad....  not rich at all... 

As the dessert is for the diner to nicely warp up the meal, it is indeed very important.  Please improve on that seriously.

Tried Sunday brunch with friends. Overall nice food, real American portion and meal. Chicken waffle a bit dry and not recommend the dessert. 
Also, Interior design with atmosphere is good for dating and friends gathering.

Good but expensive for the quantity offer...
It's quite dark inside... you might fall asleep.
Otherwise.. very nice place and good food.
The toilet doors panel are so confused. The guy is on the left side, the women on the right side. They should change the panel. The Woman one looks like a man with a pants and the Man one looks like a woman with a dress

Stylish restaurant over 2 floors in a new commercial building in the Central District. It serves a menu of "Modern British" dishes, several with games like quail, rabbit, boar, etc. Food on the whole is fairly well prepared & presented. Many steak options available but unfortunately no pork nor lamb chops. A good choice for interesting & reasonably priced western meal in Central.
Service really slow. Waiters unpleasant. Food average, expensive. Really bad price quality ratio. Forget our orders

reviews.text: 酒好喝又有新意😍

想同好友黎個格調午餐, 搵到hunter and the chase, 係上環L-Place既3及4樓🏢 

12點黎未有人🤔兩層高既樓底😮 輕柔既音樂, 淡淡的黃光加埋紅色梳化配番木色餐枱🌳 環境度滿分💯 以前3樓主要做bar 🍹 佢呢家擺枱都算寬闊, 令旺區核心保留一點CHILL😎

午餐MENU 📙 簡潔, Buffet Bar 係必定有✔️再可以係十個MAIN入面揀選同埋額外加錢要甜品🍰 

Buffett bar 除左有湯 🥣(今日係豆湯), 火腿🥓芝士🧀沙律菜🥬麵包🍞通粉咁🍝 其實要求唔高已經夠你食飽飽; 仲要食物好有誠意, 味道唔係敷衍你😍

自已主菜揀咗Suckling pig 🐽 唔係度度有得食; 西班牙🇪🇸 式燒豬做法同廣東燒味係唔一樣, Suckling Pig 係燒到表層煙韌而唔係脆香😘 但下面既肉質係長期炆到淋既質地💕當你用刀切開時, 就似用鈍既較剪開集運包咁, 要慢慢搵到虛位黎切; 記住要皮連肉一齊食💋 介乎脆同淋之間既表面, 就似厚厚既豬肉乾咬口, 下面淋身既肉充滿肉汁, 混埋伴碟既薯蓉, 係豬皮包裹下萬分邪惡😈 

朋友點既熱狗🌭 都無欺場, 見到腸仔加包上枱外, 仲有三種配料一齊黎3️⃣大大碟既薯條🍟 夾埋一齊視覺滿分🔟薯條係厚身版, 少少脆醬係表面炸到乾身, 香口熱氣係停唔到口👄 

Buffett 加個Main 真係幾滯😩舒適環境加埋美味食物, 每位大約200蚊, 係中上環黎講, 性價比好高💪💪

I like the interior decor and the dining atmosphere there.  Food in there is delicious too.... Highly recommend mixed seafood in soup and suckling pig, really nice.  Deep fries seafood, is freah, too, especially the squid.  Perfect with the dressing.

But ....... but.... dessert is the weakest part.  Chocolate cake is just like a cut brownie cubes with coconut ice cream.... really disappointed.    Strawberry cheesecake is also bad....  not rich at all... 

As the dessert is for the diner to nicely warp up the meal, it is indeed very important.  Please improve on that seriously.

Tried Sunday brunch with friends. Overall nice food, real American portion and meal. Chicken waffle a bit dry and not recommend the dessert. 
Also, Interior design with atmosphere is good for dating and friends gathering.

Excellent service and great brunch price and food!

星期天是brunch date day，前幾次吃了酒店的brunch，這次試一下Hunter & The Chase的brunch，價錢只是$248一位呢！這個價錢已經包括了前菜共四款、每人一款主菜、任食Caesar Salad及薯條、還有一款甜點呢！一踏入餐廳已感覺到員工都很有禮貌又很attentive。

4-cheese mac ‘n cheese balls

兩人共有四顆芝士通粉波波，芝士味濃郁，而且很飽肚呢！

Fried head cheese sticks & marinara dip

這個裡面原來是豬肉，所以我不吃，但配上番茄醬很特別呢！

Balsamic glazed wagyu beef skewers

賣相一流的和牛串燒，非常惹味呢！

Italian cold cuts & beetroot cured salmon

三文魚非常好吃，不會過乾或過鹹，油分十足。我一向不太愛吃cold cuts但這個也蠻不錯，我也一直吃。

吃到這其實已經飽了七八成，前菜實在給得太大方了！

Grilled USDA prime hanger steak 

主菜第一款要了牛排，medium rare。賣相一流，都切好了也方便進食。醬汁是南美的chimichurri醬，很罕見的配搭呢。

Coq au vin fried chicken & waffles

第二款主菜則要了chicken & waffles，這個的特別之處是雞肉有使用紅酒醃製，會變得更鮮嫩。上菜的時候簡直把我們嚇呆了，會不會太大份呢？兩層的窩夫加兩大件的炸雞，再配上maple syrup，真的是一流的享受。

Seasonal fruit plate

最後甜點選了水果及蛋糕。水果沒有什麼特別，但都很鮮甜。

Rich chocolate cake

朱古力蛋糕則是如其名的濃郁，為這早午餐劃上完美句號。

Hunter & The Chase環境舒適、服務一流，refill水的速度是極快，每位員工都非常有禮貌。食物出品也有保證，價錢卻不會太貴，完全是物超所值呢！
